  "content": "<p class=\"max-w-prose\" style=\"max-width: 50ch;\"><em>Your personal morning show, mixing world updates, creative inspiration, and project continuity</em></p>\n<h3 id=\"core-user-context-direct-quotes\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\" href=\"#core-user-context-direct-quotes\">\n<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 14.81 17.81\" class=\"header-star inline-block mr-2\" width=\"14\" height=\"17\" opacity=\"0.2\">\n  <path d=\"M10.01,5.75c1.18-.82,2.19-1.55,3.22-2.24.48-.32,1.05-.52,1.45.07.39.58-.22.78-.54,1.07-1.15,1.05-2.29,2.12-3.46,3.14-1.61,1.41-1.68,2.82-.12,4.35.44.43.97.78,1.48,1.15.42.3.69.68.51,1.19-.2.58-.69.76-1.28.85-.87.14-1.6-1.14-2.32-.42-.47.48-.41,1.47-.65,2.2-.13.39-.52.6-.91.67-.54.1-.89-.26-1.1-.68-.37-.72-.37-1.45-.11-2.26.29-.91.9-2.19,0-2.72-.56-.33-1.53.82-2.14,1.53-.76.88-1.8,1.51-2.32,2.62-.23.48-.75.58-1.22.35-.67-.31-.56-.89-.31-1.4.71-1.44,1.94-2.43,3.1-3.46,2.66-2.37,2.68-2.36.36-5.11-.5-.6-1.05-1.16-1.57-1.74-.22-.25-.34-.56-.13-.84.2-.27.56-.24.87-.19,1.09.18,1.71,1.01,2.43,1.72.54.54,1.03,1.57,1.74,1.37.82-.24.4-1.36.48-2.08.18-1.48.32-2.95.89-4.33C8.48.27,8.7.01,9.04,0c.48-.01.69.37.72.75.07.93.1,1.87.07,2.81-.02.68-.26,1.36.17,2.19Z\"></path>\n</svg></a>Core User Context (Direct Quotes)</h3>\n<blockquote>\n<p class=\"max-w-prose max-w-prose\" style=\"max-width: 50ch;\">\"Wake up in a sunbeam, my cat is cuddling next to me, I'm well-rested and ready for the day, even a little bit bored; 'What to do?'\"</p>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<p class=\"max-w-prose max-w-prose\" style=\"max-width: 50ch;\">\"Morning coffee and spliff time is sacred; it controls the whole day, it is profoundly powerful. The things I think about, consume, and direct my intentionality towards in that time has huge impacts on my life.\"</p>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<p class=\"max-w-prose max-w-prose\" style=\"max-width: 50ch;\">\"I just wanna know the baseline stuff for my happiness; did any huge bombs go off in the world, is it going to rain today, are my friends all okay, ok, looks good, now to get to work\"</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h4 id=\"development-philosophy\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\" href=\"#development-philosophy\">\n<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 14.81 17.81\" class=\"header-star inline-block mr-2\" width=\"14\" height=\"17\" opacity=\"0.2\">\n  <path d=\"M10.01,5.75c1.18-.82,2.19-1.55,3.22-2.24.48-.32,1.05-.52,1.45.07.39.58-.22.78-.54,1.07-1.15,1.05-2.29,2.12-3.46,3.14-1.61,1.41-1.68,2.82-.12,4.35.44.43.97.78,1.48,1.15.42.3.69.68.51,1.19-.2.58-.69.76-1.28.85-.87.14-1.6-1.14-2.32-.42-.47.48-.41,1.47-.65,2.2-.13.39-.52.6-.91.67-.54.1-.89-.26-1.1-.68-.37-.72-.37-1.45-.11-2.26.29-.91.9-2.19,0-2.72-.56-.33-1.53.82-2.14,1.53-.76.88-1.8,1.51-2.32,2.62-.23.48-.75.58-1.22.35-.67-.31-.56-.89-.31-1.4.71-1.44,1.94-2.43,3.1-3.46,2.66-2.37,2.68-2.36.36-5.11-.5-.6-1.05-1.16-1.57-1.74-.22-.25-.34-.56-.13-.84.2-.27.56-.24.87-.19,1.09.18,1.71,1.01,2.43,1.72.54.54,1.03,1.57,1.74,1.37.82-.24.4-1.36.48-2.08.18-1.48.32-2.95.89-4.33C8.48.27,8.7.01,9.04,0c.48-.01.69.37.72.75.07.93.1,1.87.07,2.81-.02.68-.26,1.36.17,2.19Z\"></path>\n</svg></a>DEVELOPMENT PHILOSOPHY</h4>\n<blockquote>\n<p class=\"max-w-prose max-w-prose\" style=\"max-width: 50ch;\">\"I need to build the habit template and iterate on improving the app in a daily iterative fashion, like if I spend 15-30 minutes adding/improving features on it at the end of every day for the next morning it would grow in a slow curated careful way\"</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h4 id=\"target-user-clarity\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\" href=\"#target-user-clarity\">\n<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 14.81 17.81\" class=\"header-star inline-block mr-2\" width=\"14\" height=\"17\" opacity=\"0.2\">\n  <path d=\"M10.01,5.75c1.18-.82,2.19-1.55,3.22-2.24.48-.32,1.05-.52,1.45.07.39.58-.22.78-.54,1.07-1.15,1.05-2.29,2.12-3.46,3.14-1.61,1.41-1.68,2.82-.12,4.35.44.43.97.78,1.48,1.15.42.3.69.68.5