out new AI technique [‚Ä¶] On Instagram I stumble across a really cool reel\"</p>\n</blockquote>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p class=\"max-w-prose\" style=\"max-width: 50ch;\">Seeking inspiration but finding distraction</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p class=\"max-w-prose\" style=\"max-width: 50ch;\">Need for filtered, meaningful updates</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p class=\"max-w-prose\" style=\"max-width: 50ch;\">DOCUMENTATION CHALLENGES</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p class=\"max-w-prose max-w-prose\" style=\"max-width: 50ch;\">\"I profoundly struggle with the latter part. I think, after 32 years on this planet, it's mostly about like, not putting myself out there so I won't be 'rejected'\"</p>\n</blockquote>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p class=\"max-w-prose\" style=\"max-width: 50ch;\">PROJECT CONTINUITY</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p class=\"max-w-prose max-w-prose\" style=\"max-width: 50ch;\">\"I'll look back and over the course of the week i made like 3 weird little command line tools, a weird art thing, an animation in after effects, and a weird generative modular synth thing\"</p>\n</blockquote>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h3 id=\"interaction-pattern-considerations\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\" href=\"#interaction-pattern-considerations\">\n<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 14.81 17.81\" class=\"header-star inline-block mr-2\" width=\"14\" height=\"17\" opacity=\"0.2\">\n  <path d=\"M10.01,5.75c1.18-.82,2.19-1.55,3.22-2.24.48-.32,1.05-.52,1.45.07.39.58-.22.78-.54,1.07-1.15,1.05-2.29,2.12-3.46,3.14-1.61,1.41-1.68,2.82-.12,4.35.44.43.97.78,1.48,1.15.42.3.69.68.51,1.19-.2.58-.69.76-1.28.85-.87.14-1.6-1.14-2.32-.42-.47.48-.41,1.47-.65,2.2-.13.39-.52.6-.91.67-.54.1-.89-.26-1.1-.68-.37-.72-.37-1.45-.11-2.26.29-.91.9-2.19,0-2.72-.56-.33-1.53.82-2.14,1.53-.76.88-1.8,1.51-2.32,2.62-.23.48-.75.58-1.22.35-.67-.31-.56-.89-.31-1.4.71-1.44,1.94-2.43,3.1-3.46,2.66-2.37,2.68-2.36.36-5.11-.5-.6-1.05-1.16-1.57-1.74-.22-.25-.34-.56-.13-.84.2-.27.56-.24.87-.19,1.09.18,1.71,1.01,2.43,1.72.54.54,1.03,1.57,1.7